metadata.name: cow in the mist
metadata.description:
I was always dreaming about getting those little fellas infront of my lense but couldnt imagine that i will happen this way. 

Reading about a special place where those teddycows run around totally free made me really excited so i grabbed my camera and went on a hike. 

I will never forget that cold freezing morning when out of sudden this creature was standing right next to me slighty hidden in the fog just waiting for me to press the shutter. 

Pure joy!

1/1
